Interface PrecursorDataMap

All Known Subinterfaces:

All Known Implementing Classes:
BaseElevationMap, BaseFertilityMap, BaseSaltWaterMap, RoutingMap.RoutingInfo, SaltWaterMap.SaltWaterInfo
public interface PrecursorDataMap

A precursor data map is a "layer" of the game map. Examples of precursor maps include elevation maps and fertility map. Precursor maps are developed from other precursor, and eventually combined to form a game map.

maxwelldickey
